REMARK   3  OTHER REFINEMENT REMARKS:  COORDINATES IN THE A*BC ORTHOGONAL       
REMARK   3  FRAME ARE PRESENTED BELOW FOR FOUR MONOMERS. ONE ENZYMATICALLY      
REMARK   3  ACTIVE SOD DIMER COMPRISES MONOMERS ORANGE (CHAIN INDICATOR O)      
REMARK   3  AND YELLOW (Y). ANOTHER DIMER COMPRISES MONOMERS BLUE (B) AND       
REMARK   3  GREEN (G). FOR THE ACTIVE SITE HISTIDINES, THE PLACEMENT OF         
REMARK   3  HYDROGENS WAS AS FOLLOWS FOR X-PLOR REFINEMENT: HIS 46, 118         
REMARK   3  HAVE A HYDROGEN ON THE DELTA NITROGEN; HIS 44, 69, 78 HAVE A        
REMARK   3  HYDROGEN ON THE EPSILON NITROGEN; AND HIS 61 IS NEGATIVELY          
REMARK   3  CHARGED WITH NEITHER HYDROGEN.                                      
